- Risks and Limitations

For each point, include the reference line(s) where it came from, such as â€œ(Lines 120â€“150)â€.

Avoid repeating headings. Present it clearly and professionally, but preserve references for legal traceability.

Summaries:
\"\"\"
{combined_summary}
\"\"\"
"""
```

